like an eternity.

340
00:13:58,871 --> 00:14:02,607
How is it that I'm only
just now meeting you?

341
00:14:04,644 --> 00:14:06,277
Look, Carter, you
got to believe me.

342
00:14:06,312 --> 00:14:08,846
