anything wrong!

448
00:18:10,523 --> 00:18:13,491
(crowd clamoring in anger)

449
00:18:13,526 --> 00:18:16,794
Carter, I think this has
all kind of gone too far.

450
00:18:16,829 --> 00:18:17,795
What do you think
you're doing?

451
00:18:17,830 --> 00:18:20,097
I'm gonna make this right.

452
00:18:21,167 --> 00:18:22,833
Everyone!
Everyone!

453
00:18:22,869 --> 00:18:24,902
Listen, I have
something to say.

454
00:18:24,937 --> 00:18:27,638
Cleveland Jr. doesn't
deserve any of this.

455
00:18:27,673 --> 00:18:29,940
All those things you heard
about Cleveland Jr. were lies.

456
00:18:29,976 --> 00:18:32,343
He didn't do anything to me.

457
00:18:32,378 --> 00:18:34,612
He's a good kid,
from a good family.

458
00:18:34,647 --> 00:18:37,948
