and I did something stupid.

459
00:18:37,984 --> 00:18:40,224
I swear, it had nothing to do
with the color of his skin,

460
00:18:40,253 --> 00:18:43,454
but... I did shoot him.

461
00:18:44,824 --> 00:18:48,192
