responsible for my actions.

462
00:18:48,227 --> 00:18:50,661
Even if that means
going to jail.

463
00:18:50,696 --> 00:18:51,829
You heard him,
other cops.

464
00:18:51,864 --> 00:18:53,597
Let's take him in.

465
00:18:53,633 --> 00:18:55,065
He doesn't know
our names, does he?

466
00:18:55,101 --> 00:18:56,700
I don't think he does.

467
00:19:00,406 --> 00:19:01,605
Wait a minute.

468
00:19:01,641 --> 00:19:03,607
Peter didn't shoot my son.

469
00:19:03,643 --> 00:19:05,175
I did.

470
00:19:05,211 --> 00:19:06,343
(crowd gasps)

471
00:19:06,379 --> 00:19:08,312
Peter was just taking
the blame for me.

472
00:19:08,347 --> 00:19:11,048
He's a good friend.

473
00:19:11,083 --> 00:19:14,385
Eh, Mr. Brown,
what exactly are you saying?

474
00:19:14,420 --> 00:19:16,420
I'm saying that I,
Cleveland Brown,

475
00:19:16,455 --> 00:19:17,888
a black man,

476
00:19:17,924 --> 00:19:19,523
shot Cleveland Brown, Jr.,

