black-on-black crime.

481
00:19:31,203 --> 00:19:33,337
Boy, the world
we live in, huh?

482
00:19:33,372 --> 00:19:35,739
Brian, reach into
Meg's pocket.

483
00:19:35,775 --> 00:19:37,141
Go ahead, Brian.

484
00:19:37,176 --> 00:19:39,843
I-I-I don't want to.

485
00:19:39,879 --> 00:19:42,079
Cleveland,
why did you do that?

486
00:19:42,114 --> 00:19:45,182
Peter, since this is about
racism, why don't we take

487
00:19:45,217 --> 00:19:49,119
a slow, hands-clasped-behind-
the-back walk together?

488
00:19:49,155 --> 00:19:51,322
Listen, I know you wouldn't
have shot Cleveland Jr.

489
00:19:51,357 --> 00:19:53,257
